        "func": "// POOL Heating — data collect trigger (60s).\n// V B2 vsechno ctene v decision func z global.get (homeassistant state).\n// Tento node zatim jen trigger propaguje. V pripadnych optimalizacich (B3)\n// by sem slo pridat pre-fetch a aggregaci.\nmsg.payload = {ts: Date.now()};\nreturn msg;\n",
